title: Wrong file dimension when calling maybe_download function
body_html: Inside 1_notmnist.ipynb file maybe_download function is called twice and fails twice because of a wrong file dimension. For notMNIST_large.tar.gz file right dimension should be 74250249, and for notMNIST_small.tar.gz file right dimension should be 6381568. PS: working on mac
